title: Yahoo Lifestyle
text: Hit the gas when the green flag waves to start the race today. It is easy enough to identify exactly what it is that you aspire to accomplish. But you dont want to start out cold when there is so much at stake and the competition is so fierce. Preparations, training, and practice make you a force to be reckoned with now. And pointers from friends or loved ones who are experienced at running this track can be like icing on the cake. With this kind of hyper-readiness, the prize youre after is well within your reach.
